body:
Fail fast at startup with validated config:

@Validated + @ConfigurationProperties

Bad YAML? App won't start. That's a feature.

code:
@Validated
@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "app")
public class AppProperties {
  @NotBlank private String name;
  @Min(1) @Max(60) private Integer timeout;
}

@Valid
private Security security;

public static class Security {
  @NotBlank private String username;
  @NotBlank private String password;
}

body:
Validate lists in application.yml:

@NotEmpty
private List<@NotBlank String> servers;

Empty server list → startup failure.

Load test data in integration tests with one annotation:

@SpringBootTest + @Sql("/test-data.sql")

No @BeforeEach seeding boilerplate.

